                      "ep_id": 7084,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/15/237301566/693da8a1b01352fde999598e49b34fde_541324707221914524.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Элементальные драконы",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Xiuhcoatl is a Pyro Dragon.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7419,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Gosoythoth",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7368,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "menu_id": 7,
                      "name": "Lord of Eroded Primal Fire",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Reaper of the Abyss has managed to extract the remnant will of Xiuhcoatl from the memories contained within the earth's ley lines. The dragon is trapped in the final day of its existence, and its boundless fury has consumed all reason.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7074,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/08/237301566/e7f7eee058f60fc225b1f5bc654a08e0_7006634286090563879.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Шбаланке",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Xbalanque defeated Xiuhcoatl in the Great Volcano of Tollan and was reborn from the fire, becoming the first Pyro Archon.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7297,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Ваксаклахун Уба Кан",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Sage of the Stolen Flame wanted his son,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7296,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Och-Kan",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", to defeat Xiuhcoatl and become the next Dragon Sovereign.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 6584,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/02/70239714/5709594dc5a9060e80eff1f292116304_6487538755070721421.png",
                      "menu_id": 7,
                      "name": "Кукузавр-тиран золотого пламени",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7013,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/16/237301566/63ce79e5312eda1c2946bde7b80c7727_7540709973449326147.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Малыш",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7296,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Оч-кан",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Dragons and Saurians with the Flamelord's Blessing mark possess incredible power, but modern Saurians can no longer withstand it today. The Wayob and the Night Kingdom also reject this power and refuse to accept such Saurians. In the process of growing, they will sometimes be killed by this power, or driven mad by it. Legend has it that the tribal warriors would carry a token that was split in two, and in the Great Volcano of Tollan, they would wash the name of their companion as remembered by the Fallen Dragon.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7267,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Золотое прошение",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 6875,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/07/124137736/558e5a31d367a67a8e85745a668d2c5e_9156352436265891527.png",
                      "menu_id": 9,
                      "name": "Золотое прошение",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "According to legend, the ancient Dragonlord transformed one of his eyes into a conduit of supreme authority by which all flames might be governed. When Xbalanque defeated the Pyro Dragon, he split the dragon's eye into two.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
